Explanation: 
The paper presents a new algorithm for constructing decision trees, which falls under the sub-category of Rule Learning in AI. The paper also discusses the theoretical aspects of the algorithm and presents empirical results for various domains, indicating the presence of Theory in the paper. The other sub-categories of AI (Case Based, Genetic Algorithms, Neural Networks, Probabilistic Methods, Reinforcement Learning) are not directly relevant to the content of the paper.
